metadata.name: Naffiti VIP NFT Pass on Ethereum
metadata.description: At Naffiti, we want to ensure you can experience all that we have to offer and receive the best privileges while you are with us. With the Naffiti VIP NFT Pass, you can enjoy a cherrypicked selection of exclusive benefits, including guaranteed whitelist for designated NFT sales, access to members-exclusive events, exclusive airdrops of NFTs, giveaways of electronic gadgets, gaming devices, vouchers, as well as limited-edition merchandise (official Naffiti merch, exclusive NFT collections, etc.).
